title: Encore (1951) S. Maugham Glynis Johns Nigel Patrick
description:
Three part movie presenting short stories by Somerset Maugham,introduced by himself. I find that Gigolo and Gigolette is by far the best, thus I have separated the three - you can watch the its you like best. G&G tells the story of a woman who does high diving to amuse casino audiences, and her hidden fears.

Maugham is always interesting - I also have Trilogy and Quartet, if anyone wants.
